N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 23 ยง 201.8 - Authority of the Superintendent Preserved

State Regulations

Nothing in this Part shall be construed to limit or affect
the superintendent's authority under to the Banking Law, the Insurance Law, the

Financial Services Law, or any other statute or regulation. Notes
